title: [The Workery]
description: The mildly sweet scents of water lily and jasmine suffuse the air with their freshly laundered scents.  Intricately embroidered wall hangings cover the polished bulkheads, and star-cut brass oil lamps hang from the beams above, swaying lightly with the movements of the ship.  Halfling clerks in sunny-colored aprons flit around the trunks of merchandise, ready to assist customers.
